parameters: It seems there are no traps in this area.

This is no time for "hey there"!! Seriously, you're such an
idiot, idiot, idiot!!

Really... I was so worried about what I would do if Kohane-
chan didn't come back... I've been worried this whole
time... sniff... sob...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[10]Hisana-chan... I'm really sorry for making you worry...

...Yeah, I'm okay now. Sorry for making you worry in return.
So you managed to deactivate the barrier, right?

Got it! I'm on my way there with the Guardians' strike
force, so just wait a little longer, okay?

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]That's great! But I also destroyed the secret weapon that
the Liberator had prepared, so if we can just suppress that
guy "Belial," everything should be okay, I think!

...That's good to hear... but since it's called the
Guardians' annihilation operation, I have a feeling there's
still something else. Be careful until we get there.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Okay! Then I'll do what I can to scout out any remaining
forces until Hisana-chan arrives!
I never imagined you'd make it this far!

The Guardians' troops will be arriving soon as well. Rest
assured, preparations to welcome them are in place.

If you want to know, then come to me. Amy is also waiting
for you.
For now... yes. But traitors must be dealt with, after all.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]...So I have no choice but to go, huh.
That's right, you'd better hurry before it's too late!
It seems like there's still something going on.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]I have to go! Amy-chan might be in danger!

She's the Liberator girl who helped you, right? I think
she's beyond the underground plant, so hurry and go to her!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]The underground plant... It's past the room where I fought
with Amy-chan. Got it!
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = B
"Let's thwart Belial's ambition in the\nunderground plant."
